name: Layout Fix MBTI Personality Insights AI: A/T & % Analysis
description: Layout Fix An AI-powered application to discover your MBTI personality type (-A or -T) with percentage breakdowns for each dichotomy. Explores suitable career paths, organizational roles, educational directions, and receives personalized self-improvement suggestions based on your self-description or a dynamic Q&A. Integrates concepts like David Hawkins' Map of Consciousness and New Age literature for deeper, actionable insights for growth.
